不符，簡直歪理連篇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21371212_1581309715264765_9044857249435216554_n.jpg?oh=23359fbee3eddf3a65a91a02fa2d4515&amp;oe=5A5E2759\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21371212_1581309715264765_9044857249435216554_n.jpg%3Foh%3D23359fbee3eddf3a65a91a02fa2d4515%26oe%3D5A5E2759&h=7d099d63&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那共產黨夠無公投上台啦，咪又係代表13億支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c85a35e3c907cf07b502728063c0e32e3f0f44","tid":390862,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"搞返個「第1條關注組」<br />\n<br />\n同泛民個45條關注組睇齊<br />\n<br />\n拉埋佢地落水"},{"pid":"ac2265f7a8771d6559f1844f03af8c759f428970","tid":390862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc57d85e24f1287446f0960c502e0593d5f3524","tid":390862,"uid":20659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"修改變成：<br />\n香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國可分離的部分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30486b6672b7f664611a5836763b3fb9580123a","tid":390862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>修改變成：<br />\n香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國可分離的部分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都無任何法律 (包括宗主國憲法), 寫明話第1條唔改得<br />\n<br />\n法理上, 條條都改得"},{"pid":"d42dbdea803e5ac5ef2be2715bdce99bb9070230","tid":390862,"uid":48060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:08:21